## Frame Receiver

The receiver is a TCP server.
You should be able to give the IP address and port number trough a config file or by using parameter.
The Frame Receiver should be ready to receive frame in the raw format describe in the precedent section.

## Frame Transmetter

The receiver is a TCP client.
You should be able to give the IP address and port number trough a config file or by using parameter.
The Frame Transmetter should be able to transmit frame depending of the FPS given in parameter of the application.

## Data Receiver

The data Receiver is on the same side of the Frame transmetter. It's also a client.
It should be able to extract data from the received trame and to compare it with the annotation file.

## Data Transmetter
